<plot>Richie's life long dream is to move to Tahiti. He has his passport, he has his plane ticket, but he also has one last night on the job as a security guard. He is closer than ever to fulfilling his dream, but when he stumbles upon a robbery in progress, Tahiti seems farther away than ever. He must decide whether to intervene or run away to his tropical island paradise.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?384285</url></doc>
